Libyan Rebels Plan Major Attack on Mountain Town, Reuters Says

-- B y   B l a n c h e   G a t t
-- 
2011-07-27T19:45:29Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-27/libyan-rebels-plan-major-attack-on-mountain-town-reuters-says.html
Libyan rebels are planning a major
offensive on the town of Ghezaia in the western mountains close
to the Tunisian border “tomorrow or the next day,” Reuters
 reported , citing rebel commander Omar Fakkan.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Blanche Gatt in London at 
 bgatt@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
